- Don't come in. Get out!

139
00:08:45,820 --> 00:08:46,900
- Get out, get out!
- Quickly!

140
00:08:47,220 --> 00:08:48,260
- Don't come in!
- Get out!

141
00:08:48,340 --> 00:08:49,980
- Out, quickly!
- You two jerks!

142
00:08:49,980 --> 00:08:50,980
How dare you come here!

143
00:08:51,300 --> 00:08:52,620
