149
00:09:01,580 --> 00:09:02,500
Get them out.

150
00:09:02,700 --> 00:09:04,380
Get out, quickly.

151
00:09:04,700 --> 00:09:05,540
Wait.

152
00:09:07,540 --> 00:09:08,820
I don't know them.

153
00:09:09,300 --> 00:09:10,500
How can you not?

154
00:09:10,660 --> 00:09:12,180
I'm your cousin.

155
00:09:14,460 --> 00:09:15,300
Yeah.

156
00:09:15,660 --> 00:09:16,900
