158
00:09:23,700 --> 00:09:25,380
What are you waiting for?

159
00:09:25,380 --> 00:09:26,580
Get these two out of here.

160
00:09:26,880 --> 00:09:28,340
How strange.

161
00:09:29,100 --> 00:09:30,180
