165
00:09:41,060 --> 00:09:41,900
Jun Mo.

166
00:09:44,500 --> 00:09:45,340
Jun Mo, is it?

167
00:09:45,540 --> 00:09:46,580
I'm her cousin.

168
00:09:46,620 --> 00:09:47,460
